  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promotion of healthcare rights and entitlements for Armenian population</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project aims at health rights protection through increasing communities&apos; awareness on their health rights, behavioral change promotion, and state bodies accountability enforcement in Armenia. Project supports the rural people living in poverty in accessing quality and free PHC as a health right in the frame of PHC reform delivery with special focus on women health rights and lobbying for state health budget /expenditure. Project will act as an advocacy platform to push the Government to increase State budget to health sector in GDP and priorities healthcare need of socially valuable groups, including women.</narrative>
  </description>
